Angelillo https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Angelillo 0 Antonio Valentín Angelillo (Italian pronunciation: [andʒeˈlillo]; 5 September 1937 – 5 January 2018) was an Italian Argentine football forward who played the majority of his professional career in the Italian Serie A, and was a member of both the Argentine and the Italian national teams.
